Class ChenileConfiguration

java.lang.Object
org.chenile.core.model.ChenileConfiguration
public class ChenileConfiguration extends Object
The core class that contains the entire ChenileConfiguration. This contains the configuration information from chenile.properties as well as a reference to all the configured services and events in Chenile
Author:
Raja Shankar Kolluru
